Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 雖然這般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回憶也會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:59.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被時間之沙掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:03.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而變得曖昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:10.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}說著「命運」這詞是如此廉價
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而與我一同開懷大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:20.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:25.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定會將自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐漸忘卻在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}與你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也請留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成為無法集齊的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:43.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那無法尋覓的最後一片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:54.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
